DialogueNode.dialogue: Oh hey Alex, everything's fine. I was just filling out this IT ticket.
Someone from the next floor down crashed the prod server, so I have to reboot it and pull the latest stable build from the repo.
More of an annoyance than anything.
I honestly have no idea what you just said.
I should get back to work now.
I should get back to work, but we'll talk later! Have a good one!
